https://ibnishak.github.io/Timimi/

Plugin for [[Firefox]] (and as of May 02, 2020 also Chrome) that lets you edit and save [[TiddlyWiki]] files locally. It also keeps a tower-of-hanoi backup rotation if the html file. Nice.

